        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Notum sit omnibus sanctae et catholicae aecclesiae filiis, <persName
                            key="#Princeps #parentOf #grandparentOf" ref="#people/3001"
                            >Richardum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principem</rs>
                        <rs key="#grandparentOf">avum</rs> meum <rs key="#Churches">aecclesias</rs>
                        et <rs key="#Monasteries">monasteria</rs> dilexisse, <rs
                            key="#Private_foundations"><rs key="#Monasteries">cenovia</rs>
                            construxisse</rs>, inter quae etiam et <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Immunity #Monasteries #Private_foundations"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3046">Sancti Angeli quod dicitur in
                            Formis</orgName> fecisse, eumque <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                                ><rs key="#Churches">ecclesiis</rs>, <rs key="#Coloni/tenants"
                                >hominibus</rs>, <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs
                                key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                                key="#Forests #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >silvis</rs></rs> ac diversis opibus ditasse. Quo defuncto, <persName
                            key="#Princeps #parentOf" ref="#people/3002">Iordanum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principem</rs>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">patrem</rs> meum omnia quae eidem monasterio prephatus
                        Ricardus princeps <rs key="#parentOf">pater</rs> eius avus meus dederat
                        confirmasse ipsumque post modum quam plurima eidem caenovio contulisse. Ego
                        autem <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/3010">saecundus
                            Richardus</persName> divina ordinante clementia Capuanorum <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, pro salute animarum predictorum principum
                        Richardi scilicet avi et Iordani patris mei et meae, ac ob statum mei
                        principatus, <rs key="#Intercessory">interventu</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #Other_palatine_officer #fidelisOf"
                            ref="#people/4254">Ivonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">aeconomi</rs> mei, et <persName
                            ref="#people/4242" key="#Intercessory #fidelisOf">Rodolfi de
                            Mucegrossa</persName> meorum baronum et dilectorum <rs key="#fidelisOf"
                            >fidelium</rs>, per hoc videlicet principale scriptum, in perpetuum, in
                        prephato monasterio Sancti Angeli, subdito <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti Benedicti
                            Montis Casini</orgName>, cui domnus <persName
                            key="#Cardinals #Abbots #Personal_rank" ref="#people/2416"
                            >Oderisius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> et <rs key="#Cardinals">cardinalis</rs> sancte
                        Romanae aecclesiae preest, damus, tradimus concedimus ac confirmamus
                        quicquid olim <persName><name ref="Iohannes Maledictus">Iohannes Maledictus
                            </name></persName>cum <persName key="#marriage"><name ref="Maria"
                                >Maria</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#marriage">uxore</rs> sua in prenominato monasterio per <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio">cartulam oblationis</rs> dederunt et optulerunt.
                        Quin etiam in predicto monasterio Sancti Angeli simili modo in perpetuum do,
                        trado, concedo et confirmo in <rs key="#City_territory">territorio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#City_territory" ref="#places/571"><geogName
                                ref="#estates/1913" key="#City_territory"
                            >Suessano</geogName></placeName>, in loco <placeName ref="#places/2852"
                            >Balognu</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">unum villanum meum</rs>,<persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes Cinnamus"> Iohanne Cinnami</name></persName> nomine
                        cum <rs key="#childOf">filiis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >terris et universis suis pertinentiis</rs>, ad faciendum et
                        persolvendum ipse et filiis suis et heredibus suis in prenominato monasterio
                        omne <rs key="#Census">censum</rs> et <rs key="#Datium">dationes</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Public_exactions">puplicalia et scaditiones et alia omnia quae
                            parti rei puplice facere et persolvere debent aut debuerint</rs>. Item
                        in prephato monasterio per hoc videlicet principale scriptum, in perpetuum
                        concedo et confirmo unum <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Ports"
                            >portum</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Mills #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >sedium de molendinis</rs> quae est in <placeName key="#Mills #Ports"
                            ref="#places/4549">Trifisco</placeName> inter sedium salicis et sedium
                        ulmi cum<rs
                            key="#Mills #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            > duo molendina</rs> quae sunt in una <rs key="#Residences">domo</rs>
                        edificata, et cum <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >aquis et <rs key="#Riverbed">alveis</rs> et <rs key="#Shores"
                                >ripis</rs></rs> ex utraque partibus, et cum <rs key="#Roads"
                            >viis</rs> intrandi et exeundi in eis et cum omnibus earum pertinentiis.
                        Quam et <rs key="#Intercessory">per interventum</rs> domni <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Prevosts #Personal_rank" ref="#people/4245"
                            >Saxonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Prevosts">prepositi</rs> eiusdem monasterii Sancti Angeli, et
                            <persName key="#Intercessory"><name ref="Grimaldus de Sancta Iusta"
                                >Grimoaldi de Sancta Iusta</name></persName>, et <persName
                            key="#Judge" ref="#people/4255">Petro</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs>, concedo et confirmo per hoc videlicet
                        principale scriptum in prenominato monasterio Sancti Angeli, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">omnes terras</rs> quas homines predicti
                        monasterii emerunt aut infiduciaverunt legaliter ab ominibus <placeName
                            key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capuae</placeName>, videlicet tempore
                        patris mei, vel mei de illis dico quos habitantes sunt in <placeName
                            ref="#places/4528">Sarzano</placeName> et in <placeName
                            ref="#places/4530">Battitizzu</placeName>. Haec omnia predicta qualiter
                        hic supra sunt adnotata, una cum omnibus quae inferius et superius invenitur
                        esse in ipsis terris, et cum viis intrandi et exeundi in eis, ego prenotatus
                        saecundus Richardus Capuanus princeps in prenominato monasterio Sancti
                        Angeli per hoc videlicet principale scriptum do, trado, concedo et confirmo
                        ad possessionem et potestatem et dominationem predicti domni Sassonis
                        venerabilis propositis eiusque successorum, faciendo exinde utilitatem
                        eiusdem monasterii. <rs key="#Immunity">Remota omni contrarietate et
                            molestatione omnium successorum meorum vel viceprincipum, comitum vel
                            vice comitum, iudicum, sculdahorum, castaldeorum aliorumque omnium
                            mortalium persona</rs>. Quod si quis huius nostrae dationis,
                        traditionis, concessio ac confirmationis paginae contemptor aut violator in
                        aliquo esse presumpserit, <rs key="#Penalty">quinquaginta libras auri
                            purissimi</rs> persolvat: medietatem omnipotenti Deo, et predicto
                        monasterio Sancti Angeli et domno prenominato Sassoni venerabili preposito
                        eiusque successoribus; et medietatem meo sacro palatio. Solutaque paena
                        librarum, haec mea datio, traditio, concessio, et confirmatio firma, munita
                        atque inviolabile maneat in perpetuum. Et ut hoc principale scriptum firmius
                        credatur et diligentius ab omnibus observetur, manu propria illud
                        corroboravi et mei sigilli impressione iussi insigniri. (M) Ex iussione
                        prephate serenissime potestatis, scripsi ego <persName key="#Judge"
                            ref="#people/3012">Quiriacus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs>. In anno dominicae incarnationis millesimo
                        nonogesimo nono, et nono decimo anno principatus ipsius domni secundi
                        Richardi <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosi</rs> principis
                        Capuae. Datum <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capuam</placeName>,
                        mense novembrio per indictionem septimam. </ab>
                </div>
